===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{context|Australia|Canada|US|lang=en}} A road designed for safe, high-speed operation of motor vehicles through the elimination of [[at-grade]] intersections, usually divided and having at least two lanes in each direction; a [[dual carriageway]] with no at-grade crossings, a [[motorway]].
